    "notableMoments": "Episode 250# (first episode was May 27, 2020)\n- Talk about Jason Concepcion as a pioneer in this type of podcasting\n- Jason C does an incredible Imperial Probe Droid impersonation\n- This movie brought back the era of the Movie Sequel, and then ROTJ ushers in the era of the Movie Trilogy - a new business paradigm\n- This movie turns Vader into the greatest Bad Guy in cinema\n- \"I am your father\" - One of the greatest shockers in cinema history\n- Han and Leia are the greatest love story\n- Duleck's Division - When Luke goes in the Cave\n- Letters - First letter for T, Then we go into the #250 Letters segment - Silly (Xray Vision hosts set up What If?), Mr Java (To All The Hosts We've Loved Before song with Animal Mother), Bog Pod (by birria), Animal Mother (by Lizzen), Lizzen (by Ethan), Truthsayer (by Animal Mother), Kev (by Corey) and Corey (by Kev)",
