    "notableMoments": "Dune Awakenings Talk - Jason started Escape Hatch guild, Haitch is negotiating the purchase of a PC\n- Jason institutes a perminant ban on the phrase \"5 Inch Chubbies\"\n- Jason ripped his pants \"from balls to butthole\" - this spawned some excellent photoshop work in Discord\n- Lots of talk about non-standard orifices in this episode, on both sides of the issue\n- 2nd Cronenberg film on the pod (after Dead Zone)\n- Jason's first note - \"What if the TV fucked you?\"\n- The practical effects - Accumicon Helmet, Breathing TV, Oozing VCR, Clay Wall, flesh gun - really worked\n- Lots of talk about \"Slits\" - Corey is a fan\n- Howard Shore - 3rd film to score. He's been Cronenberg's guy ever since\n- Letters - Animal Mother, Truthsayer, Kev, Mr Java (Closer NIN cover), Silly Oswald (Voicemails caused the podcast and not the reverse)",
